{"tha-ap460:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap460:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap460:0.3":"Jatipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap460:1.1":"“Parinibbute bhagavati, ","tha-ap460:1.2":"padumuttare mahayase; ","tha-ap460:1.3":"Pupphavatamsake katva, ","tha-ap460:1.4":"sariramabhiropayim. ","tha-ap460:2.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap460:2.2":"nimmanam agamasaham; ","tha-ap460:2.3":"Devalokagato santo, ","tha-ap460:2.4":"punnakammam saramaham. ","tha-ap460:3.1":"Ambara pupphavasso me, ","tha-ap460:3.2":"sabbakalam pavassati; ","tha-ap460:3.3":"Samsarami manusse ce, ","tha-ap460:3.4":"raja homi mahayaso. ","tha-ap460:4.1":"Tahim kusumavasso me, ","tha-ap460:4.2":"abhivassati sabbada; ","tha-ap460:4.3":"Tasseva pupphapujaya, ","tha-ap460:4.4":"vahasa sabbadassino. ","tha-ap460:5.1":"Ayam pacchimako mayham, ","tha-ap460:5.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap460:5.3":"Ajjapi pupphavasso me, ","tha-ap460:5.4":"abhivassati sabbada. ","tha-ap460:6.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap460:6.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap460:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap460:6.4":"dehapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap460:7.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap460:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap460:7.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap460:8.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap460:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap460:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap460:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap460:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap460:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap460:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma jatipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap460:11.1":"Jatipupphiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}